                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8851" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1357</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1613 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“在商言商”还是“知恩图报”：中小民企“中顺船舶”的 融资决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot; Business is business &quot; or &quot; Repay kindness with kindness &quot;: The Financing decision-making of small and medium-sized private enterprises Zhongshun Ship </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">邓德强，季浠，周钰，赵堃瑜，秦婧婧，张佳</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南京林业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南通中顺船舶机械有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小民企融资；企业价值评估；控制权风险；儒商精神</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Financing of Small and Medium-sized Private Enterprises；Enterprise Value Evaluation；Control risk；the Spirit of Confucianism Business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在我国儒家文化的长期浸润下，一部分民营企业家在管理决策中不仅遵循着“在商言商”的商业基本行为逻辑，更深受“知恩图报、仁义礼利”的儒商精神影响。作为我国国民经济发展和社会发展的重要支柱，中小民营企业一直面临着融资渠道窄、融资难度高等难题。本案例以南通中顺船舶机械有限公司经历的“先融资、后撤资”事件为切入点，探寻在不满足股权回购请求权构成要件的情况下，创始股东同意其他股东撤资的背后原因，并通过股权融资中的企业价值评估、股权比例确定到股东撤资的退出路径选择等一系列决策过程，揭示资金供求关系、控制权风险和“知恩图报”的儒商精神对企业家融资决策的影响，从而为研究中国中小民企的融资决策影响因素提供借鉴思路。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Under the long-term infiltration of China&#39;s Confucian culture, some private entrepreneurs not only follow the basic business behavior logic of &quot; business is business &quot; in their management decisions, but are also deeply influenced by the Confucian spirit of &quot; repay kindness with kindness , benevolence, righteousness, courtesy, and benefit&quot;. As an important pillar of China&#39;s national economic development and social development, small and medium-sized private enterprises have been facing the problem of large capital demand and high financing difficulty. This case takes the &quot;financing first, then divestment&quot; incident experienced by Nantong Zhongshun Marine Machinery Co., Ltd. as the starting point, explores the reasons behind the founding shareholders&#39; consent to the withdrawal of other shareholders without meeting the constitutive requirements of the right to claim for equity repurchase, and reveals the impact of capital supply and demand, control risk and the Confucian spirit of &quot; repay kindness with kindness&quot; on entrepreneurs&#39; financing decisions from a set of financing decisions, such as the enterprise value evaluation, the determination of equity ratio and the selection of exit path for shareholders&#39; withdrawal. This paper provides a reference for the study of the influencing factors of financing decisions of small and medium-sized private enterprises in China.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1. 知识传授层面：使学员掌握中小民营企业融资时的融资渠道选择、企业价值评估方法、股权比例确定以及股东撤资时的退出路径选择相关知识点；
2. 价值引领层面：使学生更好地理解具有中国特色的企业家精神，儒商精神，并深刻理解“德不孤，必有邻。夫施德者贵不德，受恩者尚必报”的儒家思想文化，从而在复杂的商业环境中树立正确的价值观和道德观。</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8851" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看案例使用说明</th>
